flowchart LR
  A[Google Sheets or fallback questionnaire source] --> B[Normalized questionnaire table]
  B --> C[Runtime questionnaire state]
  C --> D[Participant completes the survey]
  D --> E[In-memory response assembly]

  E --> F[Numeric answers by item_id]
  E --> G[Text and context answers]
  F --> H[Factor computation]
  H --> I[Current self-scores in memory]
  I --> J[Immediate feedback]

  subgraph Store[Durable storage]
    K[submission metadata]
    L[response_numeric]
    M[response_text when enabled]
    N[score rows]
    O[peer comparison cache]
  end

  E --> K
  F --> L
  G --> M
  H --> N
  K --> O
  M --> O
  N --> O

  O --> P[Peer comparison inputs]
  P --> J

  subgraph Export[Distribution outputs]
    Q[Public anonymized bundle]
    R[Private full bundle]
  end

  K --> Q
  L --> Q
  N --> Q
  K --> R
  L --> R
  M --> R
  N --> R
